data.description: Welcome to Katy Lakes! This Castlerock "Emerson" Silver Series Floor Plan is a MUST SEE! This Home has 2 Bedrooms & 2 Baths on the First Floor along with a Flex Room / Home Office. The Downstairs Second Bedroom is Nicely Tucked Away in the Front of the Home for Privacy. The Beautiful Kitchen Boasts Quartz Countertops, a Large Prep Island, 42" Cabinets & Stainless Appliances including Refrigerator. The Primary Suite has 3 Large Windows for Lots of Natural Light. Primary Bathroom with Separate Shower, Soaking Tub, Double Sinks, & a Large Walk-in Closet! Upstairs offers a Game Room, Two Additional Bedrooms & Another Bathroom. Nestled on a Quite Cul-de-Sac Street with a Pool Size Backyard and Extended Covered Patio. Residents enjoy the Community Amenities -- Splash Pad, Swimming Pool, Cabana, Picnic Areas, Playgrounds, Walking Trails and Lakes. Close to Up and Coming New Restaurants and Shopping in This Fast Growing Part of Katy. Don't Miss This Opportunity...Call Today for a Private Tour!
